{"tid":2189721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［Now好波］97年6月 港府印俾中外傳媒參考既文件：香港政治制度按「三權分立」建立 行政、立法和司法各自獨立運作","createTime":"2020-09-05T05:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T04:52:53.000Z","uid":48083,"like":202,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"f3ea9a38e216d73bc115611ad72cce7c137cd5d8","tid":2189721,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T05:52:52.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】香港有沒有三權分立再次引發社會討論。根據97年回歸時政府派發給中外記者的文件，香港的政治制度是按照「三權分立」原則建立。有學者表示，教學時會參考不同文獻，不會只根據政府的說法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dgBz5Zt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdgBz5Zt.png&h=4fbb5e14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0L8OqZw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0L8OqZw.png&h=ab35c036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有一份港府在97年6月印製，回歸典禮時派給中外記者，介紹香港的背景資料。「政府體制」章節指，香港的政治制度是按照「三權分立」原則建立，有一個行政主導的政府。<br />\n<br />\n「三權分立」是指行政、立法和司法機關各自獨立運作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=404417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404417&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs40YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=72a3ab9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404417&h=d228f2dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=404417</a>"},{"pid":"38145aadc967b82311bf1ccf275109b8c059776c","tid":2189721,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T05:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8919f6a39e4893a4887df61d345537db27365402","tid":2189721,"uid":346260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T05:53:50.000Z","msg":"唔該借個位嚟