e","tid":2189721,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:46:55.000Z","msg":"明朝嘅劍斬清朝嘅官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf4d2a1c38aa89a6d64d2abadf16b97f0de7867","tid":2189721,"uid":139173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:48:35.000Z","msg":"所以違反中英聯合？<br />\n日落英國幾時有實質行動<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19598eb462947e0f07c72abc9d463c5ba97c9114","tid":2189721,"uid":120499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:49:08.000Z","msg":"所有港共政府真係好鍾意不斷矮化自己，明明回歸之後訂製嘅制度全部廢晒，根本就係戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家就俾人挖起啲瘡疤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e378ffcfd7f3154cdfeb7844df69c23b1535ce8f","tid":2189721,"uid":39808,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:51:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>在三權分立下，立法權、司法權、執法權（或曰行政權），互相獨立，互相制衡，能防止政府專權以致借法律之名，行逞兇之實。孟德斯鳩認為，當一個政府把持任何兩權，人民、社會的自由都會陷入危機：<br />\n舉例說，當一個政府手握&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n立法＋執法&rarr; 政府將暴虐地立法、暴虐對執法，社會變得專制；<br />\n執法＋司法&rarr; 法官擁有壓迫者的力量，可任意鎮壓民主，鐵腕整治異見者；<br />\n立法＋司法&rarr; 以法律限制人民，專制管治公民的生命和自由。<br />\n若政府統管三權，孟德斯鳩更直接的說：「一切都完了。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n瞄準大肚婆去射<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gt7vcGq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGt7vcGq.gif&h=f4aa793b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c0bf726cb40c61d7d3d7ea89aea3770e197636a","tid":2189721,"uid":205927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:53:51.000Z","msg":"中共話唔係就唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3eef332728adda393ef28446b63a6ea43a99d6","tid":2189721,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71bba69a2ebe18816951cf8fd8f2880b9b37d29","tid":2189721,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:01:19.000Z","msg":"推 你做文宣佢又做文宣，點解都係connect唔到外國人? - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2188915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2188915</a>"},{"pid":"c118cad5a67a4fa24d978200f13fbb1874248cb3","tid":2189721,"uid":11663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18eff686ac88a27064efaf34db9eb7237d1faa3e","tid":2189721,"uid":352851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T05:57:38.000Z","msg":"因為係97年6月所以唔承認<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkg